(Answer using one of the following forms: \( \sigma <  rac{1}{2}\left(1 +  rac{\pi}{2}
ight) \), \( \sigma >  rac{1}{2}\left(1 +  rac{\pi}{2}
ight) \), \( \sigma >  rac{1}{2}\left(1 + \pi
ight) \), or \( \sigma =  rac{1}{2}\left(1 +  rac{\pi}{2}
ight) \).)

